        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-01-24T19:29:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ Civil Rights Amendments Act of 2003 - Amends the Civil Rights Act of 1964 to prohibit discrimination on the basis of affectional or sexual orientation with respect to: (1) public accommodations; (2) public facilities; (3) federally assisted programs; (5) equal employment opportunities; (6) housing sales and rentals; and (7) brokerage services.]]></text>
      </summary>
